function bounceOut(t) {
  var a = 4.0 / 11.0
  var b = 8.0 / 11.0
  var c = 9.0 / 10.0

  var ca = 4356.0 / 361.0
  var cb = 35442.0 / 1805.0
  var cc = 16061.0 / 1805.0

  var t2 = t * t

  return t < a
    ? 7.5625 * t2
    : t < b
      ? 9.075 * t2 - 9.9 * t + 3.4
      : t < c
        ? ca * t2 - cb * t + cc
        : 10.8 * t * t - 20.52 * t + 10.72
}

module.exports = bounceOut
